{"tid":2083850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快必只係一個淨係識嘩眾取寵既小人政棍","createTime":"2020-06-29T04:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T06:38:13.000Z","uid":99856,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"63bdd9aac7f3240d5aef8f8e1c431613a77111dc","tid":2083850,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:32:49.000Z","msg":"不斷用把口講到自己幾勇武幾勇武<br />\n肚腩痴張揮春/人地埲牆度當做撚左野<br />\n你d所謂街站不鳩知所謂 人地遊行你提早黎鳩up幾句搏拉拎光環<br />\n永遠講既野假大空思想當自己係本土派<br />\n但你連激進都講唔上但又開口埋口自己點樣被捕想拎光環 又要鬧人無賴本土派<br />\n你只係一個戀棧權位 經常性自我感覺良好既小人<br />\n呼籲大家一票不投譚德志"},{"pid":"0110342add4ad877576724c74581e01c96aeb5d4","tid":2083850,"uid":275570,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"投譚德塞都唔投一朝得志譚德志"},{"pid":"b4a0c43a08f97d05f782b96dc87a6d2b2e3f74a7","tid":2083850,"uid":128102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"佢都係留返係街算啦<br />\n入議會佢真係唔知做乜<br />\n正經論述佢又未夠班<br />\n真係黎料又驚佢玩膠變笑料<br />\n<br />\n係街繼續撚下d大陸哩咪幾好"},{"pid":"561573f1f1f570f8c5b07714d9d0936385368ee3","tid":2083850,"uid":37465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385217f28e44a35cc5b7d8f75e23aee72f8252da","tid":2083850,"uid":361332,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08b7bbc6dea85e1984939eff41681b07da0550ef","tid":2083850,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"佢唔係不嬲都係出嚟搞笑㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fc50c42268463e5245c145e9246c92b2c0c7b9","tid":2083850,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"比上不足比下有餘啦"},{"pid":"27e7452b01aab871686de6892a9eabfd5b9bca5c","tid":2083850,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T05:39:35.000Z","m